  "synopsis": "Standing on the rooftop of Gekkoukan High School, Makoto Yuuki watches the snow fall on a peaceful winter night. With a Sony Walkman in hand, Makoto puts on his headphones. The music flowing through his ears brings about the birth of spring, showing the splendor of the device.\n\nPersona 3 the Movie Meets \"Walkman\" is a short commercial depicting the clarity and beauty of Sony's high-resolution audio throughout the changing seasons.\n\n[Written by MAL Rewrite]",
